headline: Eaton increases quarterly dividend to $1.10 per share
summary: DUBLIN, February 26, 2026--The Board of Directors of intelligent power management company Eaton (NYSE:ETN) today declared a quarterly dividend of $1.10 per ordinary share, an increase of 6% over its last quarterly dividend. The dividend is payable March 27, 2026, to shareholders of record at the close of business on March 10, 2026. Eaton has paid dividends on its shares every year since 1923.
